<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1985—Subsec. (a)(1). <ref href="/us/pl/99/145/s632/b/1">Pub. L. 99–145, § 632(b)(1)</ref>, substituted “not to exceed $8,000” for “of $3,000”, and inserted provision that upon acceptance of the agreement by the Secretary, the amounts payable upon selection for training and upon completion of training, respectively, as determined under subsection (b) of this section, shall become fixed.</p>
