<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (d). <ref href="/us/pl/96/579/s2/b/1/A">Pub. L. 96–579, § 2(b)(1)(A)</ref>, (3), redesignated former subsec. (c) as (d) and substituted “<date date="1987-09-30">September 30, 1987</date>” for “<date date="1981-09-30">September 30, 1981</date>”.</p>
